{"tid":1624888,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聽到有人問點識拆路軌，其實唔使拆路軌咁高難度","createTime":"2019-10-05T05:11:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-08T17:01:33.000Z","uid":326856,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"99288e4268ab75a1059d40ab578e112aa9806424","tid":1624888,"uid":326856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:11:53.000Z","msg":"有朋友同我講聽到有人問點識拆路軌。<br />\n<br />\n佢唔驚有人真係拆路軌，因為真係唔易，最怕被人拆／被人搞訊號系統，咁癱瘓鐵路就好易好多，佢怕大家無咗黨鐵返唔到工。<br />\n<br />\n每次黨鐵大範圍服務受阻係因為咩事？多數都係訊號系統問題<br />\n<br />\n佢話邊條線都好，路軌轉線位側邊一定有一嚿point machine，得把爛鬼鎖鎖住，[siz<span style=\"color: red;\"></span>e=2]千祈唔好！千祈唔好！千祈唔好！[/size=2]打爆把鎖，將佢由auto mode 打去Manuel mode，或者搵嘢整彎佢郁個point 嘅parts ，之後再打爛佢，<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jBt2Tav.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjBt2Tav.jpg&h=1017a61e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而西鐵馬鐵就比較易<br />\n兩條路軌中間有條好似Lan 線嘅嘢沿住全條線拉<br />\n行過[siz<span style=\"color: red;\"></span>e=2]千祈唔好！千祈唔好！千祈唔好！[/size=2]踩凹佢，甚至成條扯出嚟掉埋一邊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TgxK6xS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTgxK6xS.jpg&h=3a89226e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外沿路側邊會有好多黃色盒同埋axle counter，都係訊號系統嘅嘢，[siz<span style=\"color: red;\"></span>e=2]千祈唔好！千祈唔好！千祈唔好！[/size=2]扑爛晒佢，不過睇落好硬淨<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rF7rAr3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrF7rAr3.jpg&h=21476aac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡單嚟講，邊條線都係被人搞axle counter 同埋point machine 都會好麻煩，西鐵馬鐵就加多條線，所以佢想我幫佢提醒大家[siz<span style=\"color: red;\"></span>e=2]千祈唔好！千祈唔好！千祈唔好！[/size=2]亂嚟。<br />\n<br />\n參考文章：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkrail.fandom.com/wiki/%E4%BF%A1%E8%99%9F%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkrail.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2F%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E8%2599%259F%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E7%25B5%25B1&d=7dvrOEG19ciDDWAi8ijlqojsSVnKafjD5u%2BKhFsBKzQ%3D&h=dd6b2eb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkrail.fandom.com/wiki/%E4%BF%A1%E8%99%9F%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1</a><br />\n<br />\n另一樣想提大家嘅係，黨鐵站地面，有時有Ｄ唔知要嚟做乜嘅門，除非度門寫住係咩電房呀，咩集體呀呢Ｄ字眼，其他嘅麻煩當係黨鐵站嘅後樓梯，好多都可以喺大堂或控制室直達地面，如果個站收埋一堆兵突然衝出嚟嘅話，一定gg。<br />\n<br />\n最後，係我自己想講嘅<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港！時代革命！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"ad662b1d76310d5f21644ef7977623d9ebb16389","tid":1624888,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:12:48.000Z","msg":"［警世］請正名今日唔係休息日，係文宣日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1624858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1624858</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"89f50e6ad280454229c6bf6b50cd0f23e793db8d","tid":1624888,"uid":137493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:13:16.000Z","msg":"q"},{"pid":"6e746ab22e866018cebc2f0bf2f6a3ab9b2b25fd","tid":1624888,"uid":205397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T17:01:33.000Z","msg":"推"}]}